{"tid":2158193,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"是靚晚 趣意廚 DK Pizza 初戀嘅味道","createTime":"2020-08-15T14:22:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-15T18:43:32.000Z","uid":310853,"like":28,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"71730ccad4102ce1488273c4b07d4b4c9f5b044d","tid":2158193,"uid":310853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T14:22:32.000Z","msg":"話說小弟剛收工要買嘢返屋企一個人食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後又想感受下初戀嘅味道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5Vh8Ds7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5Vh8Ds7.png&h=c3b9ccb2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n左邊係初戀烤雞 右邊係柚子蜜糖雞翼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e6ijK9H.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe6ijK9H.png&h=9ef1a4d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n雞肉都幾嫩滑 加d檸檬上去酸酸地好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qf7P7ow.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQf7P7ow.png&h=8b5edebc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n個柚子蜜糖雞翼有六隻 而且隻隻都大大隻<br />\n甜甜酸酸又脆脆地 入面d雞肉又嫩滑<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好似8:30後外賣自取有八折<br />\n不過加埋都要$107 係有d貴<br />\n但真係幾好食下 所以我都OK<br />\n<br />\n之前嗌成個餐又自取就抵好多<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rRqqFLs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrRqqFLs.jpg&h=3ef71025&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n舊圖 上次有屋企人一齊食<br />\n依到折後就$210幾<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好耐之前戒咗食Pizza Hut 之後轉食Pizza Box<br />\n點知原來都係藍<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n後尾發現 原來有依間嘢 就走咗去試<br />\nPizza 我自己真心覺得普普通通<br />\n但屋企人就覺得好食<br />\n不過上面d料算幾足料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/55Yzy6E.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F55Yzy6E.png&h=9655794a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不過佢都幾囂張 開係Pizza Hut隔離<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aHhgNsm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaHhgNsm.png&h=8b7d747b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1fd07a44b7ffaf84f91d60443632040cdcd1314d","tid":2158193,"uid":191453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T14:25:14.000Z","msg":"pizza hut<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a90d5974c5db74b274cd737bdd870894f212b6b6","tid":2158193,"uid":310853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1fd07a44b7ffaf84f91d60443632040cdcd1314d","tid":2158193,"uid":191453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T14:25:14.000Z","msg":"pizza hut<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T14:26:24.000Z","msg":"依間d雞翼真係大隻好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86884f675e201d84decd082bd4d2cd522628770c","tid":2158193,"uid":260581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T14:27:03.000Z","msg":"一個人食咁撚多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66cb69d79249e2ec351765516621a1fdc84fb74d","tid":2158193,"uid":312363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T14:27:48.000Z","msg":"唔夠色水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"058fd041ff83d4a9fd5cde23448a10291420ea7b","tid":2158193,"uid":260581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"86884f675e201d84decd082bd4d2cd522628770c","tid":2158193,"uid":260581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T14:27:03.000Z","msg":"一個人食咁撚多<img src=\"/assets/faces/norm